Congratulations!
--And Here Is Your
Jet Flight Certificate
In years to come I am sure you will look back with pride
on your "pioneer" jet flight.
It was a pleasure to have
you aboard the TWA Boeing 707, and it is a pleasure to
send you this certificate commemorating your flight.
I think you will find the certificate an attractive addition
to your "trophy" collection, ideally suited for framing and
display on your home or office wall.
TWA plans call for continued leadership in the Jet Age now
upon us.
I hope we shall have the opportunity to welcome
you aboard many more flights as TWA jet service is initiated
on more and more of our domestic and
overseas
routes.
Sincerely,
